creator: Ray Cummings; Harl Vincent; Charles W. Diffin; Lloyd Eshbach; Victor Rousseau; William Merriam Rouse
description:
LibriVox recording of Astounding Stories 11, November 1930 by Ray Cummings; Harl Vincent; Charles W. Diffin; Lloyd Eshbach; Victor Rousseau; William Merriam Rouse.
Read in English by Bill Boerst; kgon; Roxanne Weber; Greenman66
This science-fiction mag includes "The Wall of Death" by Victor Rousseau, "The Pirate Planet" by Charles W. Diffin, "The Destroyer" by William Merriam Rouse, "The Gray Plague" by L. A. Eshbach, "Jetta of the Lowlands" by Ray Cummings, and "Vagabonds of Space" by Harl Vincent. Summary by Bill Boerst
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
